Package jaron.flightgear

Provides the classes that are used to communicate with the FlightGear Flight Simulator.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
FlightGearNMEAReceiver The FlightGearNMEAReceiver class provides a TCP/IP connection to the FlightGear flight simulator (FG) via the FG NMEA output interface.
FlightGearParser The FlightGearParser is an abstract class that must be implemented by a subclass.
FlightGearReceiver The FlightGearReceiver class provides a TCP/IP connection to the FlightGear flight simulator (FG) via the FG generic output interface.
FlightGearSender The FlightGearSender class provides a TCP/IP connection to the FlightGear flight simulator (FG) via the FG generic input interface.
FlightGearXMLParser The FlightGearXMLParser is a parser for the data that is sent from FlightGear (FG) via its generic output interface.
 

Package jaron.flightgear Description

Provides the classes that are used to communicate with the FlightGear Flight Simulator.
